{"tid":1913630,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳肇始呼籲：如非必要不應再外遊","createTime":"2020-03-07T03:13:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T03:31:13.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"70226ff4e8ad6f7b4aa1acce4f2cc7dd86c09d73","tid":1913630,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T03:13:08.000Z","msg":"食物及衛生局長陳肇始，出席本台節目時表示，自特區政府對南韓、意大利及伊朗三個國家，發出紅色外遊警示，並要求從有關地區抵港人士接受強制檢疫後，已經有約100人需入住檢疫中心，大部分是參加旅行團的人士。她呼籲市民，如非必要，應延遲外遊計劃；若果有工作需要、必須到外地的話，返港後都應該戴口罩14天，盡可能不要外出。<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始又說，由上月下旬開始，當局擴展至在普通科門診都檢測病人是否受感染，目的是及早辨識徵症較輕微的受感染人士，並安排他們隔離，令他們毋須「兜兜轉轉」，可以縮短受感染至發病，以至求診的時間，截斷感染鏈。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1272044&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1272044%26csid%3D261_341&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnFT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=85fe50a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1272044&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"20bc71996cf93b7a3c6abd26001297ae24207f64","tid":1913630,"uid":54653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T03:15:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sgSQO8d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsgSQO8d.jpg&h=ec1ce4fe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Nhm94Gz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNhm94Gz.jpg&h=88cdc631&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eedd7835bf7ce6e1658e1687da3ae537e1b9aa62","tid":1913630,"uid":32577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T03:16:23.000Z","msg":"人地封晒香港先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b4842f0b35ec5c479323b264c81c12a630cf3e7","tid":1913630,"uid":304769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T03:20:47.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母，你地肯封關洗搞成咁<br />\n<br />\n脫離支那是是香港唯一出路，但絕不能直接獨立，必須先經英美託管一段時間再經公投獨立<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1913061\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1913061</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n想消滅支那，我們就要帶領支畜暴動和革命，才有機會從內部瓦解支共（輸出革命+加速主義，缺一不可）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1911527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1911527</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"000e863dd7b5804ab78ccb1333ed10b2fbba75e6","tid":1913630,"uid":103156,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T03:28:39.000Z","msg":"如非必要唔好上班<br />\n如非必要唔好出街<br />\n如非必要唔好帶口罩<br />\n如非必要唔好封關"},{"pid":"ca6ae55ca0d22f90f929f4629d13eb410fab5115","tid":1913630,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T03:30:30.000Z","msg":"[選戰 = 統計學] 立法會直選，有冇七成議席，就睇你地有冇膽量<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1913635/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1913635/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"00ab7f03807d15384b34d05b7074ea540ae8e797","tid":1913630,"uid":1482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T03:31:13.000Z","msg":"對香港人黎講去旅行就係必要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}